{"tid":240912,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"勿助長代購 勿提Loreal group 第一頁有懶人包 化妝品護膚品討論區 #47","createTime":"2017-05-12T18:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T18:38:53.000Z","uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cc05703a9813b94162b2e92b525eaf4ce0fdb7b","tid":240912,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:14:42.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘港恥<br />\n勿 提 L'Or&eacute;al Group </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JdDePbnf4UA/ViANnOZUmeI/AAAAAAAAACc/p6ZxikjbZJQ/s1600/marques.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-JdDePbnf4UA%2FViANnOZUmeI%2FAAAAAAAAACc%2Fp6ZxikjbZJQ%2Fs1600%2Fmarques.jpg&h=b554f4da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>LANCOME 事件重溫</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/19/024454_1668ad4871506d20ea533a2f2a7d88c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F19%2F024454_1668ad4871506d20ea533a2f2a7d88c8.jpg&h=3a21d078&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jeVp1h7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjeVp1h7.jpg&h=da6eb5e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5068KK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5068KK.jpg&h=c30babfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/Lanc&ocirc;me取消何韻詩演唱會風波\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2FLanc%C3%B4me%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2d8ab397\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/Lanc&ocirc;me取消何韻詩演唱會風波</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">[勿助長代購] 自己化妝品自己買！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/226858/page/21?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/226858/page/21?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望連登妝post可以保持返高登幾十個post嘅良好風氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">問問題前睇清楚#1及懶人包</span></span></strong> <br />\n(e.g. 花水問題及其他熱門產品)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好Google左先 對想問嘅野有基本了解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 善用關鍵字搜尋e.g. Google打「xxx lihkg」或「xxx site:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a>」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/24/233219_8dac5aec19ea44a84168ad7bf63ba618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F24%2F233219_8dac5aec19ea44a84168ad7bf63ba618.jpg&h=4b78fabd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講清楚自己要求同基本資料<br />\n（例如：乾性皮膚想搵一隻滋潤光澤型嘅粉底霜，依家用緊XXX 覺得好乾...）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如閱讀後有其他問題可以上POST一齊討論 唔好咁懶豬做伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 懶 人 包 </span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊懶人包比人close左<br />\n宜家有新懶人包不過要比D時間重建 <br />\n格式同內容會漸漸加 希望大家等待<br />\n如果有其他絲打想幫人或者分享都歡迎PM GMAIL比波耶波囉咪 <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1fW2frHTlUG2_JSFgec9vq-5PDRLCUX7UdKJ4WrrEmxA/edit?usp=sharing_eil&amp;ts=5912df7b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1fW2frHTlUG2_JSFgec9vq-5PDRLCUX7UdKJ4WrrEmxA%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing_eil%26ts%3D5912df7b&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2a08502f\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1fW2frHTlUG2_JSFgec9vq-5PDRLCUX7UdKJ4WrrEmxA/edit?usp=sharing_eil&amp;ts=5912df7b</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家可以留意下animal testing呢樣野, 有好多香港有既品牌都有做動物測試, 例如cdp, dior, shiseido, tom ford, fresh<br />\n想知個brand係咪cruelty-free有幾個方法:<br />\n1)<br />\n如果間公司係中國有實店, 咁佢一定有test on animals, <br />\n因為呢個係中國法律永規定<br />\n2)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crueltyfreekitty.com%2Fcompanies-that-test-on-animals%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ccf3974d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/</a><br />\n3)<br />\n<a href=\"http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.peta.org%2Fcruelty-free-company-search%2Findex.aspx&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4d3bf781\" target=\"_blank\">http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx</a><br />\n4)<br />\nGoogle<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/34/48/b6/3448b68470202f865371d2fe3537c94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F34%2F48%2Fb6%2F3448b68470202f865371d2fe3537c94c.jpg&h=14033483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: violet;\"> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">溫馨提示 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為方便爬文 請大家喺加左密既包膠後面加返keywords<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外提大家唔好quote太多圖 記得順便del img code 以免金剛棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1001左果個記得copy返呢度 D 野5分鐘內好開新post啦      <br />\n謝謝大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盡量第一頁不要加密</span></span>"},{"pid":"7ed2c335a13fb65543595394fc14d99308cdbc1c","tid":240912,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:27:44.000Z","msg":"loreal group"},{"pid":"8c98e7702f7b5ec96923c7d7b0d76e9f186401ba","tid":240912,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:28:39.000Z","msg":"推呢個啦 開左兩個"},{"pid":"b67f94ba52e3afde1b7ff694e02789d4dab22f61","tid":240912,"uid":98701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c091778b1af9e10972bbc7200dd9f2395cc8ca","tid":240912,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ca0fc347e63a4dc1e1f50d7f18be6286df9dbf","tid":240912,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:25:15.000Z","msg":"想問下 個鼻長期都幾紅下 之前上網search過好似叫酒渣鼻？想問下有無方法改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\nThanks a lot"},{"pid":"d97fc8d7f889ec26c21fe9e9e37ccf387bc8f67a","tid":240912,"uid":69092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T18:38:53.000Z","msg":"一轉季就有敏感問題<br />\n有咩唔敏感的牌子洗面啊護膚品啊推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nP.s.早前試clinique個咩123step都奶嘢"}]}